OL,6,FShe and her husband Brian took him to
OL,7,Fthe Royal Hospital for Children in
OL,8,FGlasgow where he was placed in the
OL,9,FIntensive Care Unit (ICU) and at six
OL,10,Fdays old was transferred to Leeds
OL,11,FChildren's Hospital.
OL,13,FIn Leeds, he underwent tests which
OL,14,Ffound that he had Haemophagocytic
OL,15,Flymphohistiocytosis (HLH), a rare
OL,16,Fimmune disorder which had been
OL,17,Ftriggered by an enterovirus and had
OL,18,Fled to organ failure.
