OL,3,CMother urges organ donation discussion
OL,4,Cafter young son's liver transplant
OL,6,FThe family, who live in Clydebank,
OL,7,FWest Dunbartonshire, were told Zac
OL,8,Fwould need a liver transplant and he
OL,9,Funderwent the operation on July 25
OL,10,Fthat year, becoming one of the
OL,11,Fyoungest babies to have such a
OL,12,Ftransplant.
OL,14,FMrs McNab said: "He was put on the
OL,15,Ftransplant list at five weeks old, and
OL,16,Fhe was put on there on Friday night,
OL,17,Fand we got a call on the Sunday
OL,18,Fafternoon to say that there was a
OL,19,Fpotential liver for him. So he was
OL,20,Fvery, very lucky. We got that call
OL,21,Freally quickly.
