OL,6,F"They told us before we left Glasgow
OL,7,Fthat the chances of Zac getting a
OL,8,Ftransplant were really small, to the
OL,9,Fpoint where they kind of told us that
OL,10,Fwe'd be best getting family to come
OL,11,Fand see him before we left and and
OL,12,Fthat was scary.
OL,14,F"I think we just hoped that he would.
OL,15,FAnd I know how lucky he is, because
OL,16,Fthere's so many kids and adults, I
OL,17,Fguess, that don't survive waiting."
OL,19,FShe added: "He really is a miracle."
