OL,4,Cafter young son's liver transplant
OL,6,FFor his transplant, Zac received part
OL,7,Fof a liver from another child.
OL,9,FHe spent several months in intensive
OL,10,Fcare after the operation, initially in
OL,11,FLeeds until September when he was
OL,12,Ftransferred to the ICU at the
OL,13,Fchildren's hospital in Glasgow.
OL,15,FHe was then moved onto another ward
OL,16,Fand was allowed home in November 2022.
OL,18,FSince then he has made good progress,
OL,19,Fwhile still taking medication each day
OL,20,Fincluding immunosuppressants.
