OL,3,CMother urges organ donation discussion
OL,4,Cafter young son's liver transplant
OL,6,FNow aged three, Zac is an active
OL,7,Flittle boy who enjoys playing
OL,8,Ffootball, bouncing on the trampoline
OL,9,Fin his garden, attending nursery and
OL,10,Fspending time with his older brother
OL,11,FJake, aged six.
OL,13,FAs organ donation week begins, Mrs
OL,14,FMcNab is urging people to discuss the
OL,15,Fissue with their loved ones.
OL,17,FShe has been in contact with the
OL,18,Fmother of the two-year-old girl whose
OL,19,Fliver Zac received and said the McNab
OL,20,Ffamily are so grateful to her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
