OL,6,FMrs McNab said: "I think I feel like
OL,7,Fpeople don't really speak about it,
OL,8,Fand I understand why. Obviously now
OL,9,Fexperiencing the other side of organ
OL,10,Fdonation as well, it's amazing.
OL,12,F"Zac didn't have long left, he was
OL,13,Fvery, very lucky. And I think if
OL,14,Fyou're able to give the family, a
OL,15,Ffamily, any family ` or several
OL,16,Ffamilies in that little girl's case `
OL,17,Fthat hope and extra time with their
OL,18,Floved one it's just amazing."
