OL,6,FShe is glad to be in touch with the
OL,7,Fgirl's mother and said: "I think
OL,8,Funless you experience it, it's quite
OL,9,Fhard to explain, because you are so
OL,10,Fhappy that you've got your child and
OL,11,Fthat someone has been able to do that
OL,12,Ffor you, but you still have a really
OL,13,Fsad, overwhelming feeling for them too.
OL,15,F"She's such a beautiful little girl,
OL,16,Fand it's so sad that family's had to
OL,17,Fgo through that."
OL,19,FOrgan and Tissue Donation Week runs
OL,20,Ffrom September 22 to 28.
