OL,6,FThe Scottish Government's "Don't leave
OL,7,Fyour loved ones in doubt" campaign is
OL,8,Furging people across Scotland to
OL,9,Fregister their donation decision.
OL,11,FPeople in Scotland can choose to be a
OL,12,Fdonor, or to opt out.
OL,14,FIf those aged 16 and over choose to do
OL,15,Fnothing, it may be assumed that they
OL,16,Fagree to become a donor if they die in
OL,17,Fcircumstances where donation is
OL,18,Fpossible, unless they are part of an
OL,19,Fexcluded group or if donation would be
OL,20,Fagainst their beliefs.
